message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "query-identifiability: certification and minimum augmentation for identifiable conjunctive queries in multi-source integration"
abstract: >-
  Tools and experiments for certifying when a Boolean conjunctive query is
  identifiable from interface-visible views (CheckCert), prescribing the minimum
  overlap augmentation when it is not (Greedy-MinAug), and constructing explicit
  non-identifiability witnesses.
